data.description: Incredible custom 5 bedroom, 4.5 bath home near Eagle Creek Reservoir! This beautiful home features over 5,000 sq ft of living space, including a main floor "in-law" suite and a primary upstairs bedroom with 3 custom walk-in closets and "spa" bath...plus additional bedroom with bath and 2 more with jack n jill bath make this a perfect floor plan! Cozy breakfast nook with brick wall,2-sided fireplace and view of pond as well as formal dining! Two living spaces plus home office with built-ins! Recent updates include: lighting, closets, roof and paint! Every inch features upgrades! Gourmet kitchen w/ large island and upgraded appliances! Light hardwood flooring, beautiful trim, raised ceilings, 2 fireplaces...move-in condition! Oversized 3-car garage plus unfinished attic for lots of storage! Home is located with a nice pond view, screened porch and patio/decks! This home is great for entertaining or enjoying the tranquil wooded lot! Make it yours today!!
